# 🛡️ CyberKavach Club Platform

A production-grade, full-stack SaaS platform designed for managing university cyber security clubs. CyberKavach handles event registrations, real-time notifications, attendance tracking, and dynamic role-based dashboards.

## 🚀 Live Links
- **Frontend (Vercel):** [https://cyberkavachclub.vercel.app](https://cyberkavachclub.vercel.app)
- **Backend API (Render):** [https://cyberkavachclub-assignment-aubaid.onrender.com](https://cyberkavachclub-assignment-aubaid.onrender.com)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** React 19, Vite, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion, Socket.io-client
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express, Socket.io
- **Database:** MongoDB
- **ORM:** Prisma
- **Authentication:** JSON Web Tokens (JWT), bcryptjs

---

## ✨ Key Features
- **Role-Based Access Control:** Distinct interfaces and permissions for Guests, Members, and Administrators (Coordinators).
- **Event Management:** Admins can publish events; users can register, join waitlists, and track their participation.
- **Real-Time Notifications:** Live system-wide alerts powered by WebSockets (Socket.io).
- **Interactive Dashboards:** Analytics, metrics, and data visualization utilizing Recharts.
- **Attendance & Rewards:** Dynamic point tracking, badge assignments, and certificate verification.
- **Team Creation:** Form teams and squads for CTFs, Hackathons, and group assignments.

